\c 28
\s UPawuli labanye bemukelwa kuhle ngamaMelitha
\p
\v 1 Kwathi sebesindile, basebesizwa ukuthi\x + 27.39.\x* isihlenge sithiwa yiMelitha\x + 27.26.\x*.
\v 2 Labalelolizwe\x + 28.4. Roma 1.14. 1 Kor. 14.11. Kol. 3.11.\x* basiphatha ngomusa\x + 27.3.\x* ongandanga\x + 19.11.\x*; ngoba babasa umlilo, basemukela sonke, ngenxa yezulu elaseliqalisile, langenxa yomqando.
\v 3 UPawuli wasetheza umnyaba wenkuni, wa\add zi\add*beka emlilweni, kwaphuma inyoka ngenxa yokutshisa, yanamathela esandleni sakhe.
\v 4 Kwathi abalelolizwe bebona isilo silenga esandleni sakhe\x + 28.4. Roma 1.14. 1 Kor. 14.11. Kol. 3.11.\x*, bakhulumisana \add besithi\add*: Isibili lumuntu ungumbulali, othi esindile olwandle\x + Luka 13.2.\x*, ukulunga kakuvumi ukuthi aphile\x + Amos 5.19.\x*.
\v 5 Yena-ke wasithintithela emlilweni isilo, akaze ehlelwa yibubi\x + Mark. 16.18. Luka 10.19.\x*.
\v 6 Basebelindela ukuthi uzavuvuka lokuthi awele phansi ahle afe; kwathi sebelinde \add isikhathi\add* eside, basebebona ukuthi kakulalutho olubi olwenzakala kuye\x + Luka 23.41.\x*, baphendula imicabango yabo bathi ungunkulunkulu\x + 8.10. 14.11.\x*.
\s UPawuli usilisa isigulane
\p
\v 7 Kubomakhelwane baleyondawo kwakulamasimu esikhulu sesihlenge, uPubliyo ngebizo\x + 27.17. Mark. 6.21.\x*; owasemukela wasingenisa kuhle insuku ezintathu.
\v 8 Kwasekusithi uyise kaPubliyo wayelele ebanjwe luqhuqho lesisu segazi; angena kuye uPawuli, wakhuleka\x + Jak. 5.14,15.\x*, wabeka izandla phezu kwakhe, wamsilisa\x + Mark. 16.18. Seb. 19.11,12. 1 Kor. 12.9,28. Luka 13.13.\x*.
\v 9 Ngakho lokho sekwenzakele, beza labanye ababesesihlengeni ababelezifo basebesiliswa;
\v 10 abasidumisa langodumo olunengi, njalo mhla sisukayo ngomkhumbi, ba\add s\add*ethesa izinto ezidingekayo\x + 1 Tim. 5.17. Mat. 15.6.\x*.
\s UPawuli ufika eRoma
\p
\v 11 Kwathi emva kwenyanga ezintathu sasuka ngomkhumbi weAleksandriya\x + 27.6.\x*, owawuhlezi ebusika esihlengeni, ulophawu \add oluthiwa\add* \w ngoDiyosikuroyi\w**.
\v 12 Sasesifika eSirakhuse sahlala insuku ezintathu;
\v 13 sasuka lapho sahamba ngokubhoda sayafika eRegiyuma, sekudlule usuku olulodwa kwafika umoya weningizimu, safika ePuthiyoli ngosuku lwesibili;
\v 14 lapho esafica khona abazalwane\x + Joha. 21.23.\x*, sacelwa ukuhlala labo insuku eziyisikhombisa; ngokunjalo saya-ke eRoma.
\v 15 Njalo besuka lapho abazalwane sebezwile izinto ngathi\x + Joha. 21.23.\x*, beza ukusihlangabeza baze bafika eApiyi Foruma leNdlini zeZihambi eziNtathu; okwathi uPawuli ebabona, wabonga uNkulunkulu, wema isibindi.
\v 16 Sathi sesifike eRoma, induna yekhulu yanikela izibotshwa enduneni yabalindi; kodwa uPawuli wavunyelwa ukuhlala yedwa, lowebutho omlindayo\x + 24.23. 27.3.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Kwasekusithi emva kwensuku ezintathu\x + 25.1.\x* uPawuli wabizela ndawonye labo abangabakhulu bamaJuda\x + 28.17. Mark. 6.21.\x*; sebebuthene, wathi kubo: Madoda bazalwane, mina kangenzanga lutho oluphambene lesizwe\x + 28.18. 24.12,13. 25.8.\x* kumbe lamasiko abobaba\x + 6.14.\x*, ngiyisibotshwa ngivela eJerusalema nganikelwa ezandleni zamaRoma\x + 21.33.\x*;
\v 18 wona esengihlolile\x + 4.9.\x* afuna ukungikhulula\x + 26.32.\x*, ngoba kungekho kimi cala elifanele ukufa\x + 28.18. 24.12,13. 25.8.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa amaJuda ala, ngacindezeleka ukulidlulisela kuKesari\x + 25.11.\x*, kungeyisikho ukuthi ngilolutho olokumangalela isizwe sakithi.
\v 20 Ngakho ngenxa yalesisizatho ngilibizele lapha ukuthi ngi\add li\add*bone ngikhulume \add lani\add*; ngoba ngenxa yethemba\x + 23.6.\x* likaIsrayeli ngizingelezelwe\x + Luka 2.25.\x* ngaleliketane\x + Efe. 6.20. 2 Tim. 1.16. Seb. 26.29. Efe. 3.1.\x*.
\v 21 Basebesithi kuye: Thina kasemukelanga izincwadi ngawe ezivela eJudiya, futhi loba ngubani wabazalwane, esefikile, kabikanga kumbe akhulume lutho olubi ngawe.
\v 22 Kodwa sifisa ukuzwa izinto ozinakanayo wena; ngoba mayelana lalobububhazuka\x + 24.14.\x* siyazi ukuthi buyaphikiswa endaweni zonke\x + Luka 2.34. 1 Pet. 2.12. 3.16. 4.14.\x*.
\p
\v 23 Njalo kwathi sebemmisele usuku, abanengi beza kuye endlini yezihambi; owabachasisela\x + 11.4.\x* wafakaza\x + Luka 16.28.\x* umbuso kaNkulunkulu\x + 1.3.\x*, ebancenga ngezinto zikaJesu\x + 19.8.\x*\x + 1.3.\x*, ethathela emlayweni kaMozisi kanye labaprofethi, kusukela ekuseni kakhulu kwaze kwaba kusihlwa\x + 17.2,3. 26.22.\x*.
\v 24 Abanye basebekholwa izinto azitshoyo, kodwa abanye kabakholwanga\x + 14.4. 17.4.\x*.
\v 25 Kwasekusithi bengavumelani bodwa basuka bahamba, uPawuli esekhulume ilizwi laba linye \add lokuthi\add*: Wayekhulume kuhle uMoya oyiNgcwele ngoIsaya umprofethi kubobaba bethu,
\v 26 esithi: Hamba uye kulesisizwe ubususithi: Ngokuzwa lizakuzwa, njalo kalisoze liqedisise; lokubona lizabona, njalo kalisoze libonisise.
\v 27 Ngoba inhliziyo yalesisizwe seyaba buthundu, njalo bezwa kanzima ngendlebe, lamehlo abo bawacimezile; hlezi babone ngamehlo, njalo bezwe ngendlebe, futhi baqedisise ngenhliziyo, njalo baphenduke, besengibasilisa\x + Isa. 6.9,10. Mat. 13.14. Luka 8.10.\x*.
\v 28 Ngakho kakwaziwe kini, ukuthi usindiso lukaNkulunkulu\x + Luka 3.6. Luka 2.30. Roma 11.11.\x* luyathunyelwa kwabezizwe, bona-ke bazakuzwa\x + Mat. 21.41,43. Luka 2.32. Seb. 13.46,47. 18.6. 22.21. 26.17,18. 19.9.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo kwathi esetshilo lezizinto, amaJuda asuka, elokuphikisana okukhulu phakathi kwawo\x + 15.2, 7.\x*.
\p
\v 30 UPawuli wasehlala iminyaka emibili egcweleyo endlini yakhe uqobo ayeyiqhatshile, wemukela bonke abangena kuye\x + Luka 8.40.\x*,
\v 31 watshumayela umbuso kaNkulunkulu, njalo wafundisa ngeNkosi uJesu Kristu\x + 20.25.\x*, ngaso sonke isibindi, engelakuvinjelwa\x + 4.29.\x*.
